name: Composition*
description: Short pieces in 20th-century idioms for one, two and three instruments. Performance an integral part. One hour. For students admitted to Composition as a major concentration.
prerequisites: Compostion Major; TMU120H1, 121H1/TMU130H1, 131H1, 132H1, 133H1, TMU105Y1/107Y1, TMU112H and TMU113H.
